nodes.text: Keith Szarabajka (born December 2, 1962) is an American actor and voice actor who voiced the Dewback Trooper, the Rebel Infiltrator, and the TIE Fighter Pilot in Star Wars: Force Commander. He also voiced Cikatro Vizago in Star Wars Rebels.
